article.headline: Ohio 79, Austin Peay 68
article.story: CLARKSVILLE, Tenn. -- Steven Coleman scored 21 points and grabbed 10 rebounds to lead Ohio to a 79-68 win over Austin Peay on Saturday night. Jerome Tillman scored 19 points and had 14 rebounds for the Bobcats (2-0). Austin Peay (1-2) was led by Drake Reed, who scored 20 points, grabbed 12 rebounds and had five assists in the Governors' first home game of the season. Wes Channels also chipped in with 17 points, four rebounds, three assists and three steals for Austin Peay. Ohio shot 45.8 percent from the field (22-for-48) and made eight 3-pointers.
